{
  "stem": "9245.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And if you could go in, you know, our dress code was so different from the gentile population, that even without the-- the yellow sign, you know, the yellow star of David, they could've recognized us.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there were no-- there was no way of how to escape from that ghetto.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the-- the-- I'm sorry to say, it doesn't sound right, but it happens to be the honest truth.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The gentile population was so inflamed against the Jews, that if it wouldn't been for their assistance, for the Germans, many more Jews would have escaped and would have been saved.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we used to go out and stand by the gate and observe the people that were going on a-- you know, strolling the streets and just-- and just thinking, what's going to happen to us?",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had absolutely no hope.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was-- there was no relief in sight.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The-- the situation was horrible.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were an awful lot of diseases that broke out in the ghetto, because people were starving from hunger.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there was a lot of typhoid and-- and a lot of dysentery, you know, where they had diarrhea, you know?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and you-- you could see people were walking like skeletons.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And some of them were lying in the streets and dying from hunger.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Did-- did anybody try to get out or escape out?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not to my knowledge.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't-- I don't think so.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't-- I don't-- it-- as I said, it was very dangerous.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You didn't have the assistance of the outside.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And let's say, if you would have escaped, they would have, right away, turned you in.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
